<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17207] remove LocaleTest, cleanup test detection of MiniKdc incompatible Locales</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17207</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread/wkdj3xv10n670k3zh4qtf204z2qr6zpl&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread/wkdj3xv10n670k3zh4qtf204z2qr6zpl&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Purpose of this jira:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;disable LocaleTest&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;refactor Locale checking logic in LocaleTest into a new &quot;assume&quot; helper for MiniKdc tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
